                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hardy</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berne</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-05-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 28, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hardy reports that the Swiss Government has granted permission for United
                    States consular officers within its jurisdiction to exercise good offices in
                    behalf of Cuban interests, and that notification of this permission has been
                    transmitted to consuls.)</p>
            </div>
